games.howToPlayText:
The goal of the game is to destroy all zombies and monsters.
Find new weapons in the boxes.
Upgrade characters and weapons to defeat strong enemies.

Q (K) - change weapons;
W, A, S, D (arrows) - move;
E (M) - apply / activate;
F (J) - super weapon.
X, Space (L, KeyPad 0) - shooting;
Mouse - look / shoot;
For mobile devices, use touch input.

